This simulates the IHU and EXP4 for the purpose of testing and debugging      
the communication protocols laid out in "AMSAT Fox-1A: IHU to Experiment 4
Interface Control Document".

It outputs two executables each representing the IHU or EXP4, 
(dummy_ihu and dummy_exp4). 

